---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="TokiGig"
  description="Stay in control as everything changes.."
>
  <main class="overflow-x-hidden">
    <section class="sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-border-default/80 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-content items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
        <a href="/" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-text-primary">
          TokiGig
        </a>

        <nav class="hidden items-center gap-8 text-sm text-text-secondary md:flex">
          <a class="transition hover:text-text-primary" href="#platform">Platform</a>
          <a class="transition hover:text-text-primary" href="#tokiscan">TokiScan</a>
          <a class="transition hover:text-text-primary" href="#future">Future</a>
          <a
            href="https://apps.tokigig.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-default px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-white shadow-soft transition hover:bg-blue-hover"
          >
            Access App
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </section>

   <section class="relative bg-bg-default py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute left-[-8rem] top-[-6rem] h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-blue-default/10 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute right-[-6rem] top-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-blue-default/5 blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-content gap-14 px-6 py-16 md:grid-cols-[1.05fr_.95fr] md:items-center md:py-24">
  		<div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-border-default bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary shadow-soft">
            Operator-first systems
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <h1 class="max-w-2xl text-5xl font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-text-primary md:text-7xl">
              Stay ahead without losing control.
            </h1>

            <p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-text-secondary">
              TokiGig helps operators navigate changing systems, workflows, and technologies with
              clarity and confidence — so nothing falls through the cracks as things evolve.
            </p>

			<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">
  			  Most teams are reacting to change. You don’t have to.
			</p>
            <p class="max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Built for teams adapting to new tools, new systems, and new expectations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-2 sm:flex-row">
            <a
  			 href="https://apps.tokigig.com"
  			 class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-default px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-soft transition hover:bg-blue-hover hover:shadow-md active:scale-[0.98]"
			>
 			 Enter the platform →
			</a>
            <a
              href="#platform"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border-default bg-white px-6 py-3 font-medium text-text-primary transition hover:bg-bg-secondary"
            >
              See the platform
            </a>
          </div>

		<!-- ===== HERO: LIVE SYSTEM SIGNAL (10E) ===== -->
			<div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-text-secondary">
  				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    				<div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-default"></div>
    				<span>System stable</span>
  				</div>

  			<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    			<div class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-blue-default"></div>
    			<span>24 workflows active</span>
  			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- ===== END HERO: LIVE SYSTEM SIGNAL ===== -->

        <!-- ===== HERO: SUPPORTING SIGNALS (SIMPLIFIED) ===== -->
			<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-text-secondary">
  				<div>
    		<span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Calm oversight</span>
    		<span class="ml-2">A steadier way to manage change</span>
  		</div>

  				<div>
    		<span class="font-medium text-text-primary">System visibility</span>
    		<span class="ml-2">See what matters across workflows</span>
  		</div>

  				<div>
    		<span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Reliable execution</span>
    		<span class="ml-2">Operate with confidence</span>
  		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- ===== END HERO: SUPPORTING SIGNALS ===== -->

          <div class="pt-2 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary">
            Calm systems. Clear action.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-border-default bg-white p-4 shadow-soft md:p-5">
  			<div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border-default/60 bg-bg-secondary p-5 md:p-6">
              <div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-border-default pb-4">
 				 <div>
    				<div class="mb-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-text-muted">
     				  Live system state
    				</div>
    				<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary">System Overview</div>
    				<div class="mt-1 text-sm text-text-secondary">
      				  Live coordination across the platform
    				</div>
 				 </div>

  				<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border-terminal bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-text-primary shadow-soft">
    				<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-default"></span>
    				Stable
  				</div>
			</div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default/70 bg-white p-5 shadow-soft">
                  <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">Workflow Status</div>
                      <div class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-text-secondary">
                        All workflows running within expected parameters.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-default">24 active workflows</div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default/70 bg-white p-5 shadow-soft">
                  <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">System Coordination</div>
                      <div class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-text-secondary">
                        Teams and systems operating in sync.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-default"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default/70 bg-white p-5 shadow-soft">
                  <div class="text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">Recent Execution</div>
                  <div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-border-terminal bg-bg-default p-4 font-mono text-sm shadow-inner">
  					<div class="text-text-secondary">&gt; Sync system state</div>
  					<div class="mt-2 text-green-default">✓ All workflows updated</div>
				  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -right-4 hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-subtle bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary shadow-soft lg:block">
            Calm systems. Clear action.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="platform" class="bg-white py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-content px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-border-default bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary">
            Why TokiGig
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-text-primary md:text-5xl">
            A steadier system for a faster-moving world.
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-text-secondary">
            Business teams are under pressure to adapt to new technology, new workflows, and new
            expectations without losing momentum. TokiGig brings clarity, trust, and reliability to
            that transition.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-7 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">See what is changing</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Get clearer visibility into workflows, signals, and system state so change does not
              catch your team flat-footed.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-7 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Stay coordinated</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Keep people, processes, and tools aligned through one operator-focused system built for
              real execution.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-7 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Move with confidence</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Adapt faster without creating more chaos, more blind spots, or more operational
              overhead.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tokiscan" class="bg-bg-secondary py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-content px-6">
        <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-8 shadow-soft md:p-10 transition hover:shadow-md">
          <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.05fr_.95fr] md:items-center">
            <div>
              <div class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-default">
 				 Early access signal
			  </div>

			  <div class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-border-default bg-bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary">
  				TokiScan
			  </div>

              <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-text-primary md:text-5xl">
                Make sure your business is still found.
              </h2>

              <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-text-secondary">
                TokiScan helps businesses understand and adapt to emerging AI-driven discovery systems
                so they remain visible, relevant, and competitive as search behavior changes.
              </p>

              <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">
  				Search is changing faster than most teams realize.
			  </p>

			  <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-text-secondary">
  				Most businesses will not notice the shift until it affects traffic, leads, and sales.
  				TokiScan helps you stay ahead calmly, early, and with confidence.
			  </p>

              <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-secondary px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Visibility monitoring
                </span>
                <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-secondary px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Shift detection
                </span>
                <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-secondary px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Early signals
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-border-default/60 bg-bg-secondary p-5 md:p-6">
  			  <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border-default/70 bg-white p-5 shadow-soft">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-border-default pb-4">
  			<div>
    			<div class="mb-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-text-muted">
      				Live discovery state
    			</div>
    			<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary">Discovery Signals</div>
    			<div class="mt-1 text-sm text-text-secondary">
      				AI search visibility snapshot
    		</div>
  		</div>

  <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border-terminal bg-bg-default px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-text-primary shadow-soft">
    <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-default"></span>
    Monitoring
  </div>
</div>

                <div class="mt-5 space-y-4">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default/70 bg-white p-4 shadow-soft">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">Brand discoverability</span>
                      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-default">Tracked</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-text-secondary">
                      Monitor how your business appears across changing search surfaces.
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-default/70 bg-white p-4 shadow-soft">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">Shift detection</span>
                      <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-default"></span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-text-secondary">
                      Spot changes early before they become a business problem.
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-terminal bg-bg-default p-4 font-mono text-sm">
                    <div class="text-text-secondary">&gt; Check search presence</div>
                    <div class="mt-2 text-green-default">✓ Visibility scan complete</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="future" class="bg-white py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-content px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-border-default bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary">
            Direction
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-text-primary md:text-5xl">
            Built for today’s operators, with room to grow.
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-text-secondary">
            TokiGig creates the customer-facing system and operator experience. Over time, that
            foundation can expand into broader platform capabilities, community, and future Toki-OS
            development without muddying the product story today.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-7 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Credible MVP</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Launch with a clear message, trustworthy design, and a direct path into the platform.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-7 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Operational depth</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Expand into richer visibility, stronger execution tooling, and deeper system
              intelligence.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white p-7 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Future ecosystem</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-secondary">
              Grow into wider platform, marketplace, and community layers through the Toki-OS vision.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="border-t border-border-default bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-content flex-col gap-3 px-6 py-8 text-sm text-text-secondary md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
        <span>© 2026 TokiGig</span>
        <span>Calm systems. Clear action.</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>